record.recordid: Print End command panel - print.end - en
record.format.name: print.end

brief.brief: The Print.End command panel enables you to end the print routine.

detail.detail: Spool File: (file variable) Specify the spool file variable.
Schedule Report: (Boolean) Specify Determines whether to schedule printing. True means schedule to print.
Report Class For Schedule: (character) Specify the name of the schedule class, if any.
Report Expiration (for schedule): (time) Specify the report expiration time, if any.
Repeat Interval (for schedule): (time) Specify the repeat time interval, if any.
Spoolheader File: (file variable) Specify the spoolheader file variable.
You must run a print.end panel after all prints finish.
